  {
    "id": "0d42367d7148589d864415c651108b26",
    "base_name": {
      "en": "Cv list french interface",
      "fr": "Cv Liste Français Interface"
    },
    "description": {
      "en": "This image shows a user interface for managing CVs (curriculum vitae) on a website or application. The page is titled \"Liste des CVs\" which translates to \"List of CVs\" in English. Below the title, there is a brief description stating that users can create new CVs, modify existing ones, or export them as PDFs.\n\nThe main section of the page displays a table with columns labeled \"Langue\" (Language), \"Titre\" (Title), \"Dernière mise à jour\" (Last Updated), \"Statut\" (Status), \"Description du poste\" (Job Description), and \"Actions\". \n\nThere is one entry in the table:\n- Language: Français (French)\n- Title: Profil entrepreneur (Entrepreneur Profile)\n- Last Updated: 21 avr. 2026 (April 21, 2026)\n- Status: En traitement (In progress)\n- Job Description: Aucune description de poste (No job description)\n\nUnder the \"Actions\" column, there are three icons: an eye icon (likely for viewing), a pencil icon (likely for editing), and a downward arrow icon (likely for downloading).\n\nAt the top left corner, there is a logo resembling a green paperclip, and at the top right corner, there is a menu icon.\n\nFilename: \"CV_List_French_Interface.png\"",
      "fr": "Cette image montre une interface utilisateur pour la gestion des CV sur un site web ou une application. La page est intitulée « Liste des CVs »."
    },
    "steps": [
      "gemini_description",
      "image_conversion",
      "html_generation"
    ],
