  {
    "id": "8ed1ac622b6d41075a5c22ac7f9ece89",
    "base_name": {
      "en": "Parti vert campaign screenshot",
      "fr": "Parti vert campaign Capture d'écran"
    },
    "description": {
      "en": "This image is a screenshot of a webpage from the Parti Vert (Green Party) website, featuring Benjamin Rankin. The top section has a dark green background with navigation links on the left side, including \"Accueil,\" \"À propos,\" \"Priorités,\" \"Thèmes,\" \"Pourquoi Vert ?,\" \"Rejoignez,\" and \"Terrebonne.\" There is also a white button labeled \"S'impliquer\" (Get Involved) on the right side.\n\nBelow the navigation menu, there is a white section with four illustrated cards promoting different campaign messages:\n1. \"Votez pour PLUS DE SOINS DE SANTÉ\" (Vote for MORE HEALTHCARE), with an illustration of hands holding a tree with colorful fruits.\n2. \"Votez pour PAIX ET SÉCURITÉ\" (Vote for PEACE AND SECURITY), with an illustration of people hugging each other.\n3. \"Votez pour METTRE FIN À LA HAINE\" (Vote for ENDING HATE), with an illustration of hands holding megaphones.\n4. \"Votez pour RÉCONCILIATION AUTOCHTONE\" (Vote for INDIGENOUS RECONCILIATION), with an illustration of hands forming a circle around a sun.\n\nA \"Mettre en pause\" (Pause) button is located above these cards.\n\nFilename: `parti_vert_campaign_screenshot.png`",
      "fr": "This image is a screenshot of a webpage from the Parti Vert (Green Party) website, featuring Benjamin Rankin. The top section has a dark green background with navigation links on the left side, including \"Accueil,\" \"À propos,\" \"Priorités,\" \"Thèmes,\" \"Pourquoi Vert ?,\" \"Rejoignez,\" and \"Terrebonne.\" There is also a white button labeled \"S'impliquer\" (Get Involved) on the right side.\n\nBelow the navigation menu, there is a white section with four illustrated cards promoting different campaign messages:\n1. \"Votez pour PLUS DE SOINS DE SANTÉ\" (Vote for MORE HEALTHCARE), with an illustration of hands holding a tree with colorful fruits.\n2. \"Votez pour PAIX ET SÉCURITÉ\" (Vote for PEACE AND SECURITY), with an illustration of people hugging each other.\n3. \"Votez pour METTRE FIN À LA HAINE\" (Vote for ENDING HATE), with an illustration of hands holding megaphones.\n4. \"Votez pour RÉCONCILIATION AUTOCHTONE\" (Vote for INDIGENOUS RECONCILIATION), with an illustration of hands forming a circle around a sun.\n\nA \"Mettre en pause\" (Pause) button is located above these cards.\n\nFilename: `parti_vert_campaign_screenshot.png`"
    },
    "steps": [
      "gemini_description",
      "image_conversion",
      "html_generation"
    ],
